author: IGN
description:
Check out the Andy Bogard DLC Character Trailer for Fatal Fury: City of the Wolves, an action fighting game developed by SNK. Players will soon be able to access the legendary Andy Bogard as a fighter in Fatal Fury: City of the Wolves. Get a look at some gameplay of Andy's moves, abilities, and techniques as he joins the fight. Andy Bogard is launching into Fatal Fury: City of the Wolves on June 24 as part of Season Pass 1 for PlayStation 4 (PS4), PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC (Steam).

#FatalCityOfTheWolves #AndyBogard #Gaming
title: Fatal Fury: City of the Wolves - Official Andy Bogard DLC Character Trailer

author: IGN
description: Dying Light franchise director Tymon Smektala explains the Chimeras (aka boss battles) you'll fight in Dying Light: The Beast, the upcoming standalone story in the Dying Light universe that gives you the powers of The Beast as you battle the zombie hordes...and the Chimeras. Dying Light: The Beast will be released on August 22 for PC, PS5, and Xbox Series X|S. Wishlist it on Steam if you're interested: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3008130/Dying_Light_The_Beast/
title: Dying Light: The Beast – Explaining the Chimeras - IGN First

author: IGN
description: Even though it’s actually been 23 years since 28 Days Later introduced a new vision of zombie movies, 28 Years Later is here! With Danny Boyle and Alex Garland returning to the franchise they started with the Rage Virus in 2002, it’s time for a quick look back at what happened in the first 2 movies. Here’s the infected’s story so far in the form of a 28 Days, Weeks and Years Later recap.
title: 28 Days Later Recap
